    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-01-21T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-01-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="118"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d118">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wu</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chinese Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-01-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 21, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 228.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inclose the formal receipt
                    for the check for $376,300 which you were good enough to hand to me yesterday,
                    this sum being the equivalent value of the silver bullion taken in 1900 by the
                    United States troops from the yamen of the salt commissioner at Tientsin,
                    China.</p>
                <pb facs="0211" n="131" xml:id="pg_131"/>
                <p>On behalf of the Imperial Government, I beg to express to you, and through you to
                    the Government of the United States, the sincere gratification which the
                    Imperial Government feels at this friendly and just action on the part of the
                    Government of the United States.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wu Ting-fang</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
